window.bookSummaryJSON = "A Magician conference serves as the perfect cover for members of a secret magician society in this case steeped in illusion and sleight of hand.<br><br>When Rockford Security is hired to play bodyguard to high-profile magician Xavier Ballentine’s props and secrets, Blake sees it as an easy job for the youngest Rockford sibling, Garrett, to get some experience in the field. But a series of mysterious thefts and prop malfunctions prove there may be more to this job that he first thought.<br><br>Soon Garrett finds himself thrust into a world of underground intrigue and illusion where things can change in the blink of an eye. As he chases down a cold-blooded killer, he realizes there is much more at stake than just a magician’s closely held secrets, what he’s been guarding would be disastrous if it fell into the wrong hands. What started out as an easy job turns into the Rockfords most important job ever and innocent lives hang in the balance."; 
